<section id="programs" class="section bg-dark text-light">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Heading + lead -->
    <div class="row justify-content-center text-center mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h2 class="section__title mb-3 fw-semibold">
          What your support makes possible
        </h2>
        <p class="section__lead mx-auto">
          Every event, raffle, and donation helps kids and families here in
          Colorado Springs feel a little more supported and a little less alone.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Program cards -->
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <article class="card card--program h-100 p-4">
          <h3 class="card__title h5 fw-bold mb-2">Getting families to treatment</h3>
          <p class="card__body mb-0">
            When a child needs care far from home, travel shouldn’t be the thing that stops them. We help cover gas, flights, hotels, and other travel costs so families can focus on getting their kids to the treatment they need.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <article class="card card--program h-100 p-4">
          <h3 class="card__title h5 fw-bold mb-2">Keeping the lights on at home</h3>
          <p class="card__body mb-0">
Parents shouldn’t have to choose between being at the hospital and paying the bills. We step in to help with rent, utilities, and other essentials so caregivers can take time off work and stay by their child’s side.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <article class="card card--program h-100 p-4">
          <h3 class="card__title h5 fw-bold mb-2">Taking one worry off their shoulders</h3>
          <p class="card__body mb-0">
            Serious illness brings a thousand new stresses. Our events raise funds that turn into real-life support—like living expenses during long stays, help with everyday costs, and a little breathing room for families facing the hardest days of their lives.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

